1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 1=

11
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:51,759
(You want to fade
with the spring blossoms?)

12
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:55,119
(Dream on!)

13
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:02,039
(You want to end it here and now?)

14
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:07,959
I won't grant you that!

15
00:01:15,180 --> 00:01:18,300
(Half a Year Ago)

16
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:20,940
(Brothel)

17
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:27,480
(Isn't this our once-famous war hero,)

18
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:30,560
(Murong Jinghe, Third Prince of Daliang)
(Lord Weibei, Prince Jinghe?)

19
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,519
(Ever since his defeat,)

20
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:34,439
(His Majesty's ignored him for years.)

21
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,680
(Now his legs don't work,)

22
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:39,959
(and he can't even perform in bed.)

23
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:44,079
My legs may not work

24
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,879
but I'm not blind

25
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,879
and my hands still work.

26
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,760
Lady

27
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:06,640
what fun is dancing alone with a sword?

28
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:10,360
Someone come dance with her.

29
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,960
Bravo! Brilliant!

30
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:15,719
Cut her down.

31
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:19,000
Gold for whoever draws blood!

32
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:28,199
That's sharp.

33
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:28,840
Not bad.

34
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:31,199
Such grand ambition, Your Highness.

35
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,879
I'm afraid these few

36
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:35,800
are not enough to satisfy you.

37
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:37,879
Well then.

38
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,479
I'll take them all.

39
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,319
Do be careful, Your Highness.

40
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:45,879
Don't end up dying on a woman's bed.

41
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,080
(I'm Deathsworn Shiqi
of the Shadow Bureau.)

42
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,719
(I disguised myself as a dancer)

43
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:01,400
(for one purpose:)

44
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:04,159
(to get close to Prince Murong Jinghe.)

45
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,159
(Ten years ago,)

46
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,240
(the Shadow Bureau's head
killed my parents.)

47
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,080
A bunch of insects.

48
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,199
How overconfident.

49
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:14,360
(I still remember
the cedar fragrance on his body.)

50
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,759
(I infiltrated the Shadow Bureau,)

51
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:19,879
(became a Deathsworn,)

52
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:21,199
(seeking revenge.)

53
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,520
(But the Shadow Bureau's head
never appeared again.)

54
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:24,879
(Until recently,)

55
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,960
(I accidentally caught
that same scent again)

56
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,840
(on Murong Jinghe.)

57
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:32,759
(Ten years ago, he was just a child,)

58
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,560
(so he wasn't the killer.)

59
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:37,639
(But the Shadow Bureau's head
must be near him.)

60
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,680
(I can only stay by his side)

61
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,840
(if I want to find the real killer.)

62
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:44,000
All of you are highly skilled experts.

63
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,400
There are five cups of wine.

64
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:48,000
Only one is free of poison.

65
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:50,800
Pick right,
and you'll serve His Highness.

66
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:52,120
Pick wrong

67
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,120
and you die.

68
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:15,560
(Is hers the poisoned one?)

69
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,839
(If she's fine,)

70
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,399
(we're dead for sure.)

71
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,000
(Why still drinking?)

72
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,560
(Does she want to die?)

73
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,240
(What... what's going on?)

74
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,240
(What about us?)

75
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:31,360
(She drank all of ours.)

76
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:39,920
You stay.

77
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:41,600
The rest of you

78
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:42,759
get out.

79
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,759
All five cups.

80
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,079
Not afraid to die?

81
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:53,639
It won't kill me.

82
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:55,319
The poison is Lockjaw Drop.

83
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,920
But it's missing one ingredient.

84
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,000
If you truly wanted to kill,
Your Highness,

85
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,199
why bother with poison?

86
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,879
I drank all that

87
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:05,040
just to save you
the trouble of testing us.

88
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,040
Clever enough.

89
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,480
Too bad.

90
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:13,480
I hate people who act on their own.

91
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:15,319
Drag her out.

92
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,839
Your Highness! Let go of me!

93
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,399
(Chu Yiyi, Princess of Xichu)
(Jinghe,)

94
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:33,120
(Beloved Consort of Emperor Murong Che)
(come here.)

95
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:36,759
Mother.

96
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,800
(What... did he just call me?)

97
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,079
Come here.

98
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,000
Your Highness.

99
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,439
As long as you behave

100
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,680
and work for me

101
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,879
whatever you want

102
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,199
I'll give it to you.

103
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,639
I will behave, I promise.

104
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,439
But the Lockjaw Drop's poison
is highly toxic.

105
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,800
Without an antidote

106
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,319
I may lose my mobility.

107
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,519
My blood is laced with poison.

108
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,199
That's the antidote to the Lockjaw Drop.

109
00:06:21,759 --> 00:06:22,439
Lick it.

110
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:04,660
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

111
